- model_id: `MOD-ADP-045`
- status: active
- expression_or_pseudocode: `accepted = live_dry_run_ready && real_candidate_count >= 30 && selected_sample_count >= 30 && controlled_smtp_delivery_count >= 2 && production_schedule_enabled == false && release_upload_required == false && video_required == false && blocking_reasons == []`
